{"tid":1825384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］區議員請入 區議會下一步係建立真正「社區」","createTime":"2020-01-15T08:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:31:39.000Z","uid":19945,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a51bffad296f141f98975cea006dee294c39a5d2","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:33:41.000Z","msg":"區議會得勢後眾所週知係奪權奪資源既好時機<br />\n但暫時好似未見有提出將其打造為「老中青參與」<br />\n立法會選舉其實好快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依一刻要拎到對家相當數量既利益遊游離票<br />\n就靠黎緊幾個月任期<br />\n<br />\n首先第一步區議員要建立網絡<br />\n並且各位手足加入類似義工團<br />\n定期一齊參與/幫手做活動<br />\n最簡單就係探訪獨居老人/老人院<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">年青人係活動過程角色應該避免談論太多政治</span></span><br />\n主要係營造一個關心社會同中老年人既有用青年<br />\n慢慢令到個班老人家由 細既都係廢青<br />\n變成 都有好多關心社會既後生仔 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔需要改變佢地社會運動係咪搞事既觀點<br />\n只需要佢地明有一班需要社會支持既後生仔就得</span></span><br />\n但當然唔係咩都唔做啦<br />\n可以從利益入手 例如最新既$5000電視/領展等<br />\n話佢地聽其實都好你地又有電視睇<br />\n但其實明明可以慳多d錢比你地睇醫生之類<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令佢地慢慢明白政府做既野唔係完全正確</span><br />\n<br />\n另一方面，區議員可以做一d定期茶會/會友既活動<br />\n簡簡單單搵d大學生做開運動教下佢地拉筋<br />\n飲下茶包食下餅乾傾下計就得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">再交由中年及銀髮族同佢地傾下政治同社會</span></span></span><br />\n佢地出口一定岩聽過我地班細<br />\n而討論其間見到後生又幫手又同佢地傾計亦有正面作用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">言談間講下政府無理過年青人感受例如今次預算無得受惠等</span></span><br />\n令佢地擔心同覺得後生都好慘<br />\n老人家一定受軟見到班細關心佢地就覺得係乖仔<br />\n道理同你識叫阿嫲阿爺佢地就笑哂口一樣<br />\n其實可以好簡單同純粹<br />\n<br />\n當愈來愈多活動可以配合老中青參加<br />\n真正既香港人社區就會建立<br />\n成功就不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1505bdff8c6aed808d53753e24f34f966e3edea2","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"平時個d食飯活動大家都要多多參與<br />\n我相信無利益輸送下<br />\n以前100人參與既活動可以做到150人既水平<br />\n大家除左文宣 身體力行都好重要"},{"pid":"42e4880b57393b75f452adb3ad684555e8d7eb5f","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"仲有最緊要<br />\n19/1 遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68YXZnA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68YXZnA.png&h=9a425fbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15bc0ad643ce0d98dcc7b2885097bb792af8448f","tid":1825384,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"【第廿貳期牆紙】 為良知發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=2008d6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=e47ad5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVmnn56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVmnn56.jpg&h=b4f6b2a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"751a450fbcb8e31a4ca1849d9f0d589a0ad33e59","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"對老人家黎講<br />\n邊個同佢傾計邊個關心佢就係好人<br />\n而且其實如果你有做過義工就知佢地好可愛<br />\n有時都會諗點解以前唔對自己阿嫲阿爺好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8061556a46cce0635aa1ca0b4ca3fc07424c80d4","tid":1825384,"uid":16323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaebd72bf667ee45e6e8558482f24eb0dfc0b6d","tid":1825384,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"同時搞下放映會有無得諗？"},{"pid":"f980d1dedcb856d27174349d53bf86f2d07728b9","tid":1825384,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af6c3cd1fd70c883ee7d6d13141fb6420957dd94","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acaebd72bf667ee45e6e8558482f24eb0dfc0b6d","tid":1825384,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"同時搞下放映會有無得諗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔得<br />\n但短期內太明顯只會令佢地卻步<br />\n有時唔洗強行要佢地支持<br />\n令佢地唔好當後生係敵人已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6585d019e15d4e450b242dec9b19ccdfdb6ee1a7","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"班狗唔做野搞到交通唔好<br />\n又多劫案當然都要提下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee769ad3b85c5b9dd293ea65a7d3c4b4efb991a3","tid":1825384,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6c3cd1fd70c883ee7d6d13141fb6420957dd94","tid":1825384,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acaebd72bf667ee45e6e8558482f24eb0dfc0b6d","tid":1825384,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"同時搞下放映會有無得諗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔得<br />\n但短期內太明顯只會令佢地卻步<br />\n有時唔洗強行要佢地支持<br />\n令佢地唔好當後生係敵人已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"或者可以簡特別case Eg. 大肚婆/阿伯醫院比人打<br />\n相信佢地好多都未睇過"},{"pid":"bb2f68c1a19838c2b81e665d74adacbd9542d0b0","tid":1825384,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2